s.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1356280/extras/70f0a7a80844d036ce68287dba15ba98.poster.avif?t=1763466033\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1356280/extras/70f0a7a80844d036ce68287dba15ba98.webm?t=1763466033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1356280/extras/70f0a7a80844d036ce68287dba15ba98.mp4?t=1763466033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Kitaria Fables is full of friendly (and not so friendly!) citizens. Make yourself known to your neighbours and fulfil their requests. The more you bond with your new friends, the more rewards you will receive as your relationships grow!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1356280/extras/e54c0f0137d797677b43545dd9d6183d.webp?t=1763466033\" width=616 height=62 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1356280/extras/231ed835523f6400f0de735c9b4ee543.poster.avif?t=1763466033\" width=616 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1356280/extras/231ed835523f6400f0de735c9b4ee543.webm?t=1763466033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1356280/extras/231ed835523f6400f0de735c9b4ee543.mp4?t=1763466033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Kitaria Fables features a local co-op mode with Steam remote-play supported. Team up with a friend, double your firepower and use the freedom of Kitaria Fables' flexible combat system to compliment each other's strengths. <br><br>As ever, we are always appreciative of 